description:
This table was moved to isb-cgc-bq.GDC_case_file_metadata_versioned.GDCfileID_to_GCSurl_r23 and is replaced here with a view. Please see isb-cgc-bq.isb-cgc-bq.GDC_case_file_metadata.GDCfileID_to_GCSurl_current for the most current table.
Data was generated from file metadata information from the GDC release 23, April 2020. Current google cloud storage paths are mapped to file gdc ids.
More details: https://docs.gdc.cancer.gov/Data/Release_Notes/Data_Release_Notes/#data-release-230.
